snippet.title: Paranoiascape opening and gameplay, weird Playstation pinball game
snippet.description:
Design, concept, music by Screaming Mad George, a famous movie SFX person. He's been involved with such movies as Society, Beyond Re-Animator and the Nightmare on Elm Street series and it does show with this weird-ass game.

Not so surprisingly this game was only released in Japan..

http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0313608/
